to run the code automaticaly online every day
head to pythonanywhere.com
create new free account
add all the files (not directories, those will need to be created inside the page)
click "consoles"
create a new "bash"
type in the console: python3 [name of the main script].py

    if you get a smtp error for loading email program is cause
    google is blocking it.

    copy the supporturl in the error notification
    paste it in the google search
    read the solution, give/allow access to the program.
    type the same command in the pythonanywhere console.
    should work!